name: MUI for Figma v5.4.0 (Community)
description:
A free demo of a large UI kit with over 600 handcrafted MUI symbols for Figma. The components are following the Material Design guidelines.


Click on Duplicate to get your copy.


Get the full version on https://mui.com/store/items/figma-react/. You can report improvement opportunities at https://github.com/mui-org/mui-design-kits/.
